Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷減速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持既定高度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推進系統 地球航行模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 索敵系統沒有報警
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周邊未發現高危目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦當前 正取道這條航線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向失落樓蘭移動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計兩天後抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據稱各部隊正在當地集結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為向它發動總攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們抵達基地後也將參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼不慌不忙地行進 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 我是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果飛得更高 速度更快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用一天就可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為避免被軌道上空的敵人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過計算敵人的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擬定的最佳航線和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的行動一旦被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅殃及失落樓蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰目的也會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 關於抵達後的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦底發生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量紅外線反應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人襲擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星移民計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其失敗被遺留在火星圈的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱獨立國家維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球聯邦政府宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭開始 已將近70年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到從砂中發動突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂中移動的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過影像分析發現有18台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時有微弱的電子干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初步認定為集團作戰的無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外暫無發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候真佩服維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發出這麼適應地球環境的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想沒用的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這確實值得深思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們擁有比聯邦先進的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以隱身衣為代表的高科技又是從何而來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這神秘感令人欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在重在想方設法應對敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管僥倖逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號卻付出推進系統受損的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動能力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有件事讓我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有機動戰士出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛看到新來的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘武裝暴動當時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏附近航行的聯邦戰艦與敵人遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其後失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖曾派救援部隊前往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後者亦下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據遇敵戰艦最後的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人是三台機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總計兩艘戰艦和十台機動戰士被毀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部將其歸類為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真身不明的敵人部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以後稱為「幻影3」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影3…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠的亡靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這情報為什麼現在才來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 別動氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在清楚一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人肯定會捲土重來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以必須用盡能用的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 所有機動戰士更換成沙漠型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他們在談什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在那裏幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤諾亞姑姑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？你在這艘船上做衛生員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星上接到的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙這忙那的沒來得及告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能和姑姑乘上同一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高興能和爸爸還有你在同艘船上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 羅瑪麗和媽媽有消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在附近城市裏避難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐也該和她們聯繫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 無非就是叫我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做父母的都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 快逃 哈羅 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 聽見沒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 吉歐 尤諾亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難為你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身打扮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 現在忙不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂不是學過醫療嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她在我身邊幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一份工作就是照顧孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長叫我指導你 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特 接下來是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 剛來就這麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 能親眼見識洛蒂師傅的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺提高特別大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說幾遍才記住？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看模擬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被訓得挺慘的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐跟你年齡相仿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又都是新人 要好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 動手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住 時刻保持移動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握敵人位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火後也不能放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住這三點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要我這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和爺爺教的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太過重視攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡而言之就是太冒進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在教你怎麼幹掉對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在戰場求生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只守不攻沒法取勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是爺爺的教誨？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死了還談什麼勝負？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住戰鬥不只是衝鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 休息幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸躲在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還需要一陣子才能修完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說 隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就給它個下馬威嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等摸清自動炮台的部署 它想逃也難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好 在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們在檢查它的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE構築器？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 剛輸入高達迄今為止的戰鬥記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲利特先生吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看能不能造出沙漠戰需要的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然見過一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但像這樣正式問候還是第一次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫洛蒂·麥德納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船的工程主管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡那套MS對戰模擬系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和這位伍德比特跟明日野家有點緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我修過幾次你爸的高達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的爺爺是菲利特先生的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的媽媽和你的爸爸還是同一個部隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 不愧是英雄的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀輕輕駕駛高達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還那麼能打 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂先生 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫伍德比特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫吉歐·明日野 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少得意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有得意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼明日野家族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你爺爺是聯邦軍老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛過高達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當自己有多了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂師傅他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是著名的麥德納工坊的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他主動參軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一介士兵做到工程主管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論決心還是志向 你都沒法和他比！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格跟他這麼說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來 你崇拜洛蒂先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很崇拜爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 伍德比特君 想見見爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能學到不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有完沒完啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為所有人都會給你特殊待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼那麼生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 吉歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比休息前狀態的還差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺真的是個很了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特如果瞭解爺爺的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實誰也不想看到你這樣的孩子上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論有多嚴厲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想你在戰鬥中生還
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 這話從何說起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是情緒低落？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 只是分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣比較容易讓孩子安心 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 是我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行崗哨任務的喬納森機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在砂中發現移動物體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中的機師請準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(640,666)}（來了!）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的新部件如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析完成 但還在構築中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離完成還要一定時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已了 用AGE-3出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩獵時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯隊 按準備會的部署行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和喬納森 德雷克在上空吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞和奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定無人機位置後攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯 Cnanche-CUSTAM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不可以飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知敵人藏在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣只會變成活靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇他們已經去承擔這份職責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你專心摧毀無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠型也顯得行動緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐·明日野 高達出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 機體容易陷入砂裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧願放慢動作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要保持機體平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了 是高達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極品獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍它！痛扁它！殲滅它！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角洲·攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 下沉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特先生 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器 G-Hopper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 立即發射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行空中換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中換裝…機師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是開動它的話 我也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維修班不能沒有洛蒂師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他隨隨便便就能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定也能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張 細節交給自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特·甘海爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Hopper 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它呢 打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 空中換裝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為我們會看著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 快完成合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是AGE-3 FORTRESS（要塞）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住這3點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次三角洲攻擊送他歸天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持運動為的是不被敵人瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 到處亂竄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聰明的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻掌握敵人位置的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既容易躲避攻擊 也容易反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火以後也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 老夫果然沒看錯你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 大家 快躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍德比特…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我伍德比特就可以了 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安息吧 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定為你報這個仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了一台幻影3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞小姐教我的 真的很管用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台被擊落的機動戰士裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是人在駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭不是什麼值得高興的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞很少說起自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在戰爭中失去了父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妹妹也重病纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻在她面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次次為敵人傷心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人會瘋的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為勝利高興並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落樓蘭化作戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火光中映射出哀傷的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往失落樓蘭的天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為躲避敵人偵測
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持低空飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.66,0:24:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加沿途收容未能及時避難的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約要7天才能抵達目的地

